data.description: The Florida Living you always wanted is yours in the stunning home! This amazing 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom house with 2 car garage is an absolute show stopper. This home offers the perfect combination of comfort, style, and modern amenities. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan, with ample natural light streaming in through large windows. The spacious living area is perfect for family gatherings or entertaining friends, and it seamlessly flows into the dining area and kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of cabinet space for all your culinary needs. It's the heart of the home, where you can create amazing meals and lasting memories. The primary bedroom features dark bambook flooring and offers tons of privacy, complete with an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The three additional bedrooms are generously sized and offer plenty of room for family members or guests. The second bathroom is conveniently located to serve these bedrooms. Step out of any of your 3 sliding glass doors to your screened lanai and backyard area, where you can relax and unwind. The fenced-in backyard provides added privacy and is perfect for entertaining. Other notable features of this property include a two-car garage, a laundry room, and easy access to nearby schools, shopping, and dining options.
